"CONFLAGRATION" - unofficial Horus Heresy short story, written by Stephen Duxbury.

Narrated and produced by A Vox in the Void.

This piece was made possible by the Patreon members for Stephens work. Please support him to continue his fantastic work!

https://www.patreon.com/StephenDuxbury40KFiction

Thankyou for allowing me to feature your amazing music in the piece! 

Another huge thankyou to all of the channel members! Your support is always remembered. 

Vox
